column29: Protocols: Entire leaf n°6 of Arabidopsis, 25 days after germination, grown in short day condition (6h light, 18h dark) were harvested, detached and put in the dark for up to 2 days. 0d and 2d samples have been harvested in triplicate for each condition. On soil. 6 h light, 18h dark, 100umol/m2 light, 60% humidity.  RNA was extracted using Qiagen RNeays kit with a DNAse removal step. Quality of RNA was controlled by Bioanalyzer.  Truseq Stranded Total RNAseq kit from Illumina.
